---
By: Blaise Pascal
Source:
  ID: 57c5499b-c3b2-4b09-92a9-a6e977a32050
  Locus:
    Page: 117
    Verse: 17
Tags:
  - Ego/Vanity
---
We do not content ourselves with the life we have in ourselves; we desire
to live an imaginary life in the minds of others, and for this purpose we
endeavor to shine.
